title: The Funniest Memes From the 2017 Oscars
text:
The Funniest Memes From the 2017 Oscars Most Popular By Sally Holmes Feb 27, 2017 The BEST part of the Oscars? The moments that inspire the memes―and, um...there were MOMENTS . Here, the best memes from tonight:

— Diane N. Sevenay (@Diane_7A) February 27, 2017 Advertisement - Continue Reading Below "yeah, so the show is about Jack The Ripper, but he's supposed to be sexy and modern. a career man" pic.twitter.com/3ZlWlfwmWy 
— Mark Agee (@MarkAgee) February 27, 2017 Advertisement - Continue Reading Below 
— weirdo (@TheJCap) February 27, 2017 Most Popular I don't know what is happening but this is what America looks like to me these days. https://t.co/UkxGm3zn2u
